  <brief_title>Firmagon (Degarelix) Intermittent Therapy</brief_title>
  <acronym>FIT</acronym>
  <official_title>Randomized, Multicentre Efficacy and Safety Study Comparing 10 Mons vs 4 Mons Degarelix Therapy in Prolonging the Off Treatment Interval in Men With Localized Prostate Cancer Receiving Intermittent ADT for Biochemical Recurrence Following Radical Local Therapy</official_title>
